---
layout: layouts/page
---

article(class="md:px-24")
    h1(class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl mt-24 font-title font-black whitespace-pre-line")= title
    p(class="text-xl mt-1 text-gray-700 dark:text-zinc-400")= subtitle
    p(class="mt-4 text-gray-400 dark:text-zinc-500")= filters.readableDate(date)
    div(class="mt-12 markdown max-w-screen-sm")
        | !{content}
    div(class="mt-12 border p-8 rounded-xl bg-white dark:bg-zinc-800 max-w-screen-sm")
        p(class="font-bold mb-1.5 text-lg font-title") Get more like this in your inbox
        include /subscribe